query:
SELECT
                EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM price_history_locf WHERE time = $1) as start_exists,
                EXISTS(SELECT 1 FROM price_history_locf WHERE time = $2) as end_exists,
                EXISTS(
                    SELECT 1
                    FROM price_history_locf
                    WHERE time = $2 AND ma_5 IS NULL
                ) as likely_corrupted
